-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
System requirement
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. php-5.2.x or above with php-pdo
2. mysql-5.x or above
3. Apache http server with mod_rewrite enabled and overriding options enabled

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Installation:
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. Point your web server Document Root to public_html
2. provide write permission to application/config directory
3. provide write permission application/data directory
4. Visit http://example.com/install . Replace replace example.com with your actual domain name
4a. You can also install from the command line. 
    Copy the myInstallerValuesDist.php to myInstallerValues.php
    Edit myInstallerValues.php in dev/scripts/Install/ 
    Provide execute permission to dev/scripts/Install/Install.php
    Invoke dev/scripts/Install/Install.php
5. You will be asked to provide a MySQL username, password with connection info

Installation issues:
1. If you are unable to install, make sure 
application.install.status = 0
in application/config/config.ini


